data.description: *SAVE BIG WITH A SPECIAL SELLER CLOSING CREDIT TO ANY BUYERS NOT WORKING WITH AN AGENT! Welcome Home to this gorgeous home in the highly desirable Norris Reserve Subdivision. Built-in 2018, this 5 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom, and 2-car garage home offers today’s desirable features of grand interior and outdoor living spaces. With 10ft ceiling on both levels, this home feels massive. The fireside great room is open to the kitchen and the informal dining area. The kitchen is defined by beautiful cabinetry, subway-tiled backsplashes, SS appliances, including double ovens, a gas range, a walk-in pantry, and a large island with a granite countertop. Walk out to the privately fenced back yard perfect for the kids and pets to play in. You'll love the in-law suite on the main level. Retreat upstairs to an expansive owner’s suite with a luxurious bathroom with a separate tub/glass shower, double vanities, and his/her walk-in closets. The upper level also includes three additional bedrooms a full bathroom, and a large laundry room. The home offers immense street appeal with a manicured front yard and a private backyard bordered by a new fence.
